sudoku.controller

Class BoardController

  • java.lang.Object
    • sudoku.controller.BoardController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class BoardController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    This class acts as a controller class for the file 'MainBoard.fxml'. It dictates the actions for each user interaction on the GUI as well as the placement of GUI components. It adds 1 GridPane, a lower Anchor Pane and side Anchor Pane.
    Version:
    1.0
